<p>英 /ˌdɪsə'bɪləti/    美 /ˌdɪsə'bɪləti/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 残疾；障碍：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you know anyone with a <strong>mental</strong> or <strong>physical</strong> <strong>disability</strong>? 
你认识有心理缺陷或生理残疾的人吗？</p><footer>人教⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had a <strong>learning disability</strong> from an early age.
从小我就在学习方面有障碍。</p><footer>2016 天津</footer></div></div>